<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="break-in">break in</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>打断；插嘴：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>“I didn’t do it!” she broke in.
她插嘴说：“我没干那事！”</p></div>

<h4 id="2-break-into">2.★ <strong>破门而入(break into)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Burglars had broken in when we were away. 
我们外出的时候，窃贼闯进了家中。</p></div></div>